title: List of tallest buildings in Seattle
summary: Seattle, Washington, United States, the most populous city in the Pacific Northwest region of North America, has 117 completed high-rise buildings over 240 feet (73 m),[1] of which 47 are over 400 feet (120 m) tall.[2][3] An additional 65 high-rise buildings are under construction or undergoing planning and design review, as of 2016.[4]
